name: PredrinkingGames

”give me a random drinking game”

skdetail:

Invocation Name: pre drink
des:
Ask Alexa to open pre drink and give you a drinking game and it will give you one of many predrinking games from www.predrink.co.uk. 
Find the rules for each of these games online at www.predrink.co.uk.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
